OOC: Actually i do mind Zardus. Banzai-Tron used to be Treadshot, who was 
killed by Airazor. he knocked Airazor out and now Tigerhawk is fighting for 
her. This is something ive been planning for a long time.

:::Cyclonus/Scourge/Fracas/Falcon:::

::Cyclonus and Scourge are blinded by the light for a few seconds, but 
quickly recover::
Scourge: Thats it. FRACAS!
::One of Scourges guns had been on his back the whole time.  But this gun was 
more than meets the eye!::
Fracas: Hey  Scourge! What's goin' on?
Scourge: I need you to attack that bot over there.
::He points to Angel Prime::
Fracas: Got it!
::With extreme precision, Scourge fired 4 powerful blasts form Fracas at 
Angel prime::
~~~~~
::Cyclonus fires 25 rapid laser blasts at Angel prime::
~~~~~
::Falcon closes his cockpit and takes off toward Syria::

--part1_9a.11007829.27d6fb69_boundary
